extendedInfo.description: Study Psalm 2 with this app of commentaries from the best commentators such as Matthew Henry, C. H. Spurgeon and John Calvin.Read Psalm 2 from the Kings Jame's Authorised Version and then look at what each of these commentators say about the Psalm verse by verse.You can also add your own notes at any time to create your very own journal of this Psalm.If you would like to know more about the Christian faith then please visit the websites listed under More Resources.  There you will find thousands of free messages and resources to help you come to a personal faith in the Lord Jesus Christ.
